ny information  bloomberg july    am et airlines company overview of chc helicopter sa snapshot people company overview chc helicopter sa provides helicopter transportation services it offers offshore transportation search and rescue emergency medical and flight training services as well as helicopter maintenance repair and overhaul services the company is headquartered in richmond canada chc helicopter sa operates as a subsidiary of chc helicopter holding sarl  agar driverichmond bc vb acanada phone  key executives for chc helicopter sa mr karl s fessenden chief executive officer age  mr lee eckert chief financial officer age  mr william joseph amelio chief executive officer of helione canada inc and president of helione canada inc age  mr peter bartolotta president  coo  the helicopter svcs business  helione canada inc age  mr larry alexandre president of helione american support llc age  compensation as of fiscal year  chc helicopter sa key developments fourth amended reorganization plan approved for chc group ltd mar   the us bankruptcy court approved the fourth amended plan of reorganization of chc group ltd on march   the debtor has filed its fourth amended plan in the court on february   as per the amended plan administrative expense claims professional fee claims priority tax claims and other priority claims shall be paid in full in cash other secured claims shall receive cash in an amount equal to the allowed amount revolving credit agreement claims of  million will be paid in cash abl credit agreement claims of  million will recover of  of the allowed amount senior secured notes claims of  billion will recover in the range of  to  of the allowed amount unsecured notes claims of  million will recover in the range of  to  of the allowed amount general unsecured claims of  million shall receive  of the new membership interests plus up to  million in new unsecured notes less the amount of the convenience claim distribution amount of  million convenience claims